## Evaluation Metrics

Accuracy alone is not enough for credit risk prediction.

### Important Metrics Used

### Recall

High recall is important because missing a default customer can cause major financial loss.

### F1-Score

Used to balance false positives and false negatives.

### AUC-ROC

Measures how well the model distinguishes between good and bad loan applicants.

